author: kpvdr
msg: Fixed cluster store problem where second and subsequent cluster nodes (which are persistent) to join a cluster fail with a "Exchange already exists: amq.direct (MessageStoreImpl.cpp:488)" message. To do this a new method was added to MessageStore called discardInit() which will throw away all restored data (if any) and restart as though no restore had taken place.
